

- Web Design 
It refers to both the aesthetic portion of th website and it's usability. Web designers use various design programs such as Adobe Photos shop to create the layout and other visual elements of the website.


- Web development 
Developers on the other hand , take a website design and actually make a functioning website from it. Web Developers use HTML , CSS , Javascript , PHP and other programming language to bring to life the design files.


- HTML : HTML is a Hypertext markup language , used to create the layout of website.

- Hypertext is a text which contain link to other document or another text.

- Markup - Markup something to up. e.g <p>Paragraph</p>